00:40:59.656 --> 00:41:01.086 A:middle
so it won't take quite as long.

00:41:01.306 --> 00:41:02.496 A:middle
There's one file;
there's the next

00:41:03.136 --> 00:41:07.576 A:middle
and says finished
encoding, menomena.

